%e A002047             4  5  1  2  3  -( n+1) -->  1  2 -2 -1  0
%e A002047             4  2  5  3  1  -( n+1) -->  1 -1  2  0 -2
%e A002047             --------------              --------------
%e A002047            11 11 11 11 11  -(4n+3) -->  0  0  0  0  0
